   <|"Data" -> ".md\nIt can capture the following events from a window, where \
it is placed:\n- `\"Mounted\"` - when the component/window has been loaded\n- \
`\"Closed\"` - closing of a window\n- `\"Blur\"` - when a user removed focus \
from a window\n- `\"Focus\"` - when a user has focused a window\n\nThis \
component works in normal cells as well as on WLX. It does not occupy space \
and renders nothing.", "Display" -> "codemirror", 
